lution into a headless CMS powerhouse in\n                        Strapi 3.x, Strapi has consistently delivered valuable features and improvements to meet the\n                        needs of developers and content creators. </p>\n\n                    <p>Strapi will play a crucial role in shaping the future of content management. Organizations should\n                        keep in check the Strapi versions that are being launched and embrace its full potential and\n                        capabilities to stay ahead. </p>\n','Strapi Version History and Features - Addxp Technologies',NULL),(9,'Content Experience-kontent ai empowering your content management process','2023-10-03 18:00:27.412000','2024-02-05 11:56:20.394000','2023-10-03 18:00:28.735000',2,2,'Content Experience','<p>Learn from scratch all about Kontent.ai, how it works, what features and capabilities it holds\n                        and how it can enhance and empower your content management process. </p>',' <p>Effective content management processes are essential in todays digital landscape. Especially\n                        when your business is aiming at engaging, informing, and captivating their audiences. These\n                        days, Content Management Systems have become the cornerstone for achieving this goal. </p>\n\n                    <p>CMS platforms offer tools that help you streamline your content creation, content management as\n                        well as content delivery. One innovative player in the CMS market is Kontent.ai which is known\n                        to empower and elevate content management processes for businesses through the power of AI. </p>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"/kontent-ai-development-service\" class=\"common-link\">Kontent.ai</a>\n                        is a software developed by Kentico, a cloud-based CMS designed to simplify the way\n                        content is created, managed, and delivered. It has a headless architecture tha