aving happy and healthy\n              employees.</p>',NULL),(41,'Growing and Learning',NULL,'<p>Our fast-growing work environment will give you a visionary growth so much to learn, implement and\n              thrive!</p>',NULL),(42,'10+ successful projects',NULL,NULL,'<p>Our clients have always received exceptional results with their business being driven to success\n	  through our efforts.</p>'),(43,'5+ years of experience',NULL,NULL,'<p>We have an experience of over a better part of the decade working on headless technology.</p>'),(44,'In-house development',NULL,NULL,'<p>Our team is in-house and they are fully dedicated to fulfilling all of our clients\' needs\n	  religiously.</p>'),(45,'Flexible hiring approach',NULL,NULL,'<p>We don\'t have any rigid terms of contract.You pay for what you get and for how long you avail our\n	  services.</p>'),(46,'Multi-domain expertise',NULL,NULL,'<p>Our multi-talented developers bring a wealth of knoweledge and unique set of skills to the table in\n	  multiple domains. </p>'),(47,'Service Level Agreement (SLA)',NULL,NULL,'<p>Our services are guaranteed to meet the highest standards of quality with prompt and timely\n	  deliverables.</p>'),(48,'Experience speed, scalability and security like never before!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Get the Strapi Headless CMS and transform your web content management through freedom and innovation.</p>'),(49,'Lets connect and build a unique digital experience!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Leave it to us and from start to finish, well develop custom Strapi plugins catered to your business needs.\n        </p>'),(50,'Dont be outdated  get updated!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Avail our Strapi Upgrade services and get the latest version playing its charms on your website users.</p>'),(51,'Lets make your competitors wonder how you did it!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Transform your website from good to great and wow all your customers through our comprehensive Strapi\n          Migration services.</p>'),(52,'Just like Strapi, our consultations are al