ou where you can drive the\n              project as per your directions.</p>','<h5>Get the 24x7<br> Availability</h5>'),(60,'Hire Strapi CMS Developers','Why hire Strapi resources from us?','<p>We are a combination of a digital experience provider and a headless solutions creator. Launch your\n            products in the market faster with better performance through the power of self-hosted, customizable, and\n            open-source CMS. The team of Addxp is certified, brilliant, and possesses cross-functional expertise\n            required to handle projects of this caliber.</p>',''),(61,'Every pixel tells a story! Whats yours?',NULL,NULL,' <p>Lets build a dream world for your users where every interaction is filled with delight and every click\n          sparks joy!</p>'),(62,'Experience a world of fabulous finds!',NULL,NULL,' <p>A delightful customer journey and experience that makes them repeat their purchases is just one click away.</p>'),(63,'Let your imagination soar!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Create content experiences where each sentence keeps the users hooked, makes them click and brings them one\n          step closer to your brand.</p>'),(82,'Ready to unleash the power of Umbraco?',NULL,NULL,' <p>Hire Umbraco developers today and build the perfect team for your perfect business!\n        </p>'),(83,'Hire Umbraco Developers','Why hire Umbraco resources from us?','<p>We are both a digital experience provider and a headless solutions provider. Our professionals bring a\n            wealth of experience to help you build custom Umbraco-based solutions. You can get seamless website\n            development as we deliver tailor-made solutions that align perfectly with your business objectives. The team\n            of Addxp is certified, brilliant, and possesses cross-functional expertise required to handle projects of\n            this caliber.</p>',''),(84,'Hire Umbraco Developers',NULL,'<p>We provide Umbraco developers where the resources will work dedicatedly and exclusively for your project\n              with a 24x7 availability round-the-clock. You will get the resources for you where you can drive the\n              project as per your directions.</p>',' <h5>Get the 24x7<br> Availability</h5>'),(85,'Its how a CMS should be','All there is for you to know',NULL,'<p>Sitecore Experience Manager (XM) Cloud represents the cutting-edge of cloud-native Software-as-a-Service CMS solutions. It facilitates rapid software development and cloud-based content management across various channels and devices, thanks to its headless architecture.</p>'),(86,'Start giving best customer experience to your coustomer today!',NULL,NULL,'<p>Explore the core capabilities of our cloud-native CMS, including visual page editing, multilingual and multisite administration, personalized experiences, and analytics.</p>');
