bsite with stunning and\n              intuitive designs. </p>'),(12,'Contentstack<br>Development','<p>Get the futuristic and customizable headless CMS and elevate your digital presence. Simplify your content\n              management and create a robust experience. </p>'),(13,'Contentstack<br>Content Migration','<p>Migrate your content effortlessly to this agile, headless CMS and streamline all your digital operations\n              with minimal downtime.</p>'),(14,'Contentstack<br>Personalization','<p>Create experiences that are unique and engaging for each individual user by delivering the right\n              personalized content at the right time.</p>'),(15,'Contentstack<br> Commerce','<p>Elevate your online business by building seamless and flexible ecommerce experiences for your customers.\n</p>'),(16,'Contentstack<br>Upgrade','<p>Upgrade your content infrastructure with smoothness by unlocking the new features and enhancements of\n              Contentstack.</p>'),(17,'Contentstack<br>Support','<p>Get the guidance and support directly from experts for optimizing all your digital operations with\n              Contentstack support.</p>'),(18,'Hire Contentstack<br>Developer','<p>Create personalized and dynamic web applications and solutions by hiring our team of experienced\n              Contentstack developers.</p>'),(19,'Kontent CMS<br> Development','<p>Get the headless CMS Kontent and govern everything related to content. Make your brand stand out by\n              delivering exceptional digital experiences now and also in the future.</p>'),(20,'Kentico UI/UX <br> Design','<p>Build cutting-edge UI/UX design and elevate the digital experiences that you provide to your users with\n              Kentico UI/UX Design services.</p>'),(21,'Kentico<br> Consultation','<p>When it comes to any services related to Kentico, you can count on us for consulting you with some of the\n              best approaches, solutions and recommendations.</p>'),(22,'Kentico Managed<