INSERT INTO `components_base_template_long_fields` VALUES (1,'1. Information gathering','This is the initial phase where there is the discovery call to understand the client requirements. Here, we will analyze the clients business, their pain points and specific requests and needs.'),(2,'2. Recommending solutions','Based on our initial discussion, we will develop a strategy, recommend a solution and send out a proposal outlining scope, timeline, deliverables, and cost estimation.'),(3,'3. Contract & Agreement','The proposal is sent and once the client reviews it and accepts the deal, we enter into an agreement and contract that defines fully the objectives, the expectations and the deal from both parties.'),(4,'4. Onboarding the client','The very first step of the project is to onboard the client and make them familiar with the team. This also includes making the team familiar with the client requirements and objectives of the project.'),(5,'5. CMS Development','Once the Strapi CMS development starts, there will be sprint planning, daily standups, demos at intervals, scrum meetings, and regular updates about the progress being sent to the client.'),(6,'6. Deployment with testing','To ensure that the quality of the work is maintained, testing is done when deploying the project.'),(7,'7. Client approval','The completed work is then tested by the client. They will go through everything and once they are satisfied with the work, they will give us the green signal.'),(8,'8. Going live','Once the reviews are done and the client has approved the project, the website goes live.'),(9,'1. Introduction','In the initial phases, we will understand the clients\' requirements and challenges. We will also analyze their goals and expectations from us.'),(10,'2. Research','We will conduct the research required to identify the areas of improvement. We then come up with the solutions and the best approaches.'),(11,'3. Documentation','Our Strapi consultants will generate a report of our entire work from the research and analysis to the recommended solutions.'),(12,'4. Solution','We will conduct a final interview with the client to present our recommendations and solutions required for their challenges.'),(14,'1. Initiation of Ticket','The client will initiate the tickets by assigning them to the team based on pre-discussed terms.'),(15,'2. Defining Priorities','The support team will prioritize the tasks after reviewing the tickets and set targets to be achieved.'),(16,'3. Client Review','The client team and the support team will review the approach and ensure that both are on the same page.'),(17,'4. Resolving Tickets','The support team start working on resolving the tickets including QA testing to ensure there are no errors'),(18,'5. Client Approval','The client will go through the solution post which they will provide approvals and close the tickets');
