INSERT INTO `components_faq_faqs` VALUES (1,'Question1','<p>Answer1<p>'),(49,'Can Contentful be used without writing code?','<ul>\n              <li>Yes, without writing code, one can create and organize content on Contentful.</li>\n              <li>This platforms interface is designed in a way that even people from non-technical background can use\n                it.</li>\n            </ul>'),(50,'What platforms are Supported by Contentful?','<p>You can load the content on any platforms that are supporting the creation of HTTP requests and supports\n              JSON.</p>'),(51,'Which browsers are supported by Contentful?','<ul>\n              <li>Google Chrome</li>\n              <li>Mozilla Firefox</li>\n              <li>Apple Safari</li>\n              <li>Opera</li>\n              <li>Microsoft Edge</li>\n            </ul>'),(52,'Is Contentstack open source?','<ul>\n              <li>Contentstack is actually one of the leading open SaaS CMS in the market that combines the mind of\n                SaaS with the customization open source.</li>\n            </ul>'),(53,'Can you use Contentstack for multi-language content management?','<ul>\n              <li>Yes, there are robust, multi-language capabilities that allows businesses to create and manage content\n                for a global audience.</li>\n            </ul>'),(54,'Does Contentstack offer integrations with any other tools?','<ul>\n              <li>Contentstack offers integrations with a hugfe range of third-party tools and technologies that include\n                marketing automation, ecommerce plateform, analyticle tools, etc.</li>\n            </ul>'),(55,'Can I customize my website design through Umbraco?','<p>Yes, Umbraco allows you to fully design and customize your website. You can create multiple templates\n              also using HTML, CSS, and Umbracos templates.</p>'),(56,'Is Umbraco suitable for ecommerce websites?','<p>Yes, you can build ecommerce websites and also integrate Umbraco with other ecommerce platforms or\n              plugins for building robust online stores.</p>'),(57,'Can I migrate my current website to Umbraco?','<p>Yes, you can migrate your existing website to Umbraco. It is advisable that you consult with Umbraco\n              experts for a better experience and a smooth migration.</p>'),(58,'How to get started for Strapi Development?','<ul>\n             <li>You can reach <a href=\"/contact-us\" class=\"text-dark\">  out to us<span class=\"common-link\"> here</span></a> and\n                we can walk you through what Strapi development is and how we can get\n                started on transforming your business.</li>\n            </ul>'),(59,'Can Strapi be used for e-commerce?','<ul>\n              <li>Strapi is actually meant to be used the most for e-commerce. We offer a variety of Strapi related\n                services including the e-commerce platform development.</li>\n            </ul>'),(60,'What are the key features provided by Strapi?','<ul>\n              <li>API-first architecture</li>\n              <li>Access control based on roles</li>\n              <li>Supports multiple languages</li>\n              <li>Media management</li>\n              <li>Supports SQL and NoSQL databases</li>\n            </ul>'),(61,'What other types of applications can be built in Strapi?','<ul>\n              <li>Apart from ecommerce, Strapi can be used to build blogs, corporate websites, mobile applications as\n                well as single-page applications.</li>\n            </ul>'),(62,'Is Kentico suitable for small businesses?','<p>Kentico caters to both types of business, small and enterprise-level, and provides scalable solutions\n              tailored to meet the specific needs of a business.</p>'),(63,'Can you integrate Kentico with other systems?','<p>Yes, using Kentico you can integrate third party systems and applications such as CRMs, marketing\n              automation platforms, ERP solutions, etc.</p>'),(64,'Does Kontent.AI support SEO capabilities?','<p>Yes, Kontent.AI, a CMS developed by Kentico, comes with features for optimizing your content for search\n              engines and helps you increase search engine rankings and visibility.</p>'),(65,'Can Kontent.ai handle large-scale projects?','<p>Yes, it is designed to scale effortlessly for accommodating projects of any size. The platform can handle\n              high volumes of content and traffic without compromising the performance.</p>'),(66,'Does Kontent.ai have analytics and insights?','<p>Yes, it comes with inbuilt tracking capabilities and provides valuable data-driven insights in terms of\n              performance, engagement and user behavior.</p>'),(67,'How do I get started with Kontent.ai?','<p>You can explore our website or <a href=\"contact-us\" class=\"common-link\">get in touch</a> with our team\n              and discuss your specific content management needs to experience the magic of Kontent.ai today.</p>'),(68,'Is upgrading to the latest version of Strapi difficult?','<p>Upgrading can be a smooth-sailing process if you choose the right partners, in this case, experienced\n                partners. When you go for the experienced ones, they always follow the upgrade guide provided by Strapi\n                and always ensure a smooth upgradation.</p>'),(69,' Will upgrading affect the existing data?','<p>Upgrading to a different version of Strapi does not affect the existing data. However, it is always\n                recommended that you backup all of your data before upgrading to ensure there are no data losses in case\n                of a glitch or error.</p>'),(70,'Can I downgrade to a previous version of Strapi?','<p>It is possible to go back to a previous version of Strapi but it is not usually recommended as it may\n                result in compatibility issues with your existing plugins and data. Also upgrading is the way to be able\n                to leverage the latest features and functionalities which will give your website more capabiltiies.</p>'),(71,'Can I migrate from non-Strapi platforms to Strapi?','<ul>\n              <li>Yes, it is possible to migrate data and configurations from non-Strapi platforms to Strapi. However,\n                this process may vary from platform to platform.</li>\n            </ul>'),(72,'Will doing Strapi Migration affect my existing data and configurations?','<ul>\n              <li>Strapi Migration does not affect your existing data and configurations but it is always recommended to\n                back up your data to ensure there are no losses in case of any glitch or errors.</li>\n            </ul>'),(73,'How long does Strapi Migration usually take?','<p>The duration of Strapi Migration process can vary depending on the size and the complexity of the\n                website being migrated. It is usually recommended to plan time duration accordingly to ensure a smooth\n                migration.</p>'),(74,'What Strapi services can I get consultation for?','<p>You can get Strapi CMS Consulting for all of our services that include:</p>\n<ul>\n              <li>Strapi Development</li>\n              <li>Strapi Plugin Development </li>\n              <li>Strapi Upgrade</li>\n              <li>Strapi Migration</li>\n              <li>Strapi Maintenance &amp; Support</li>\n              <li>Strapi UI/UX Design</li>\n            </ul>'),(75,'Why should I consider Strapi Consulting?','<p>If you want to streamline your content and management process, our team of experts can provide you with\n              solutions based on their extensive knowledge that will enable you to save time, money and resources while\n              improving your overall approach.</p>'),(76,'Can Strapi Consulting be customized for my specific niche or industry?','<p>Yes, we offer consulting for a variety of businesses ranging in industries and niches. The Strapi\n              consultants will work on your unique business needs and recommend tailor-made solutions accordingly.\n            </p>'),(77,'Can you have multiple websites on Strapi?','<ul>\n              <li>YES, Strapi is headless so you can have multiple heads, multiple frontends, and multiple pages.</li>\n            </ul>'),(78,'What kind of a support does Strapi offer?','<li>Strapi offers various support options including a community forum, official documentation as well as\n                paid support plans.</li>'),(79,'Is Strapi a good fit for large-scale apps?','<p>Strapi is a product built on Node.js application, a database and a UI. As long as these components are\n              able to scale, the performance and the scalability are not going to be a cause of concern.</p>'),(80,'What kind of a Strapi experience do we have?','<ul>\n              <li>We have been working on headless technology for over 9 years now.</li>\n              <li>Our teams are in-house and fully dedicated to all our clients needs.</li>\n              <li>We have certified developers with expertise in multiple domains.</li>\n              <li>We have successfully delivered 10+ headless projects till now.</li>\n            </ul>'),(81,'How do we communicate and coordinate?','<ul>\n              <li>We maintain a very strong chain of communication with our partners and clients.</li>\n              <li>Our resources are always available over email as well as your preferred mode of communication.</li>\n              <li>We regularly check on the achievements and keep an eye on the updates of the project.</li>\n              <li>We have a weekly/bi-monthly meeting for discussing the project report apart from the daily scrum\n                meetings.</li>\n              <li>We always have a retrospective meeting with the client at the end of the month.</li>\n            </ul>'),(82,'How do we know we are getting the right development team?','<ul>\n              <li>We analyze the job requirements and the business goals thoroughly.</li>\n              <li>We share the profiles of all our resources with the clients.</li>\n              <li>The resource allocation is always done based on the engagement model selected by the client.</li>\n              <li>We also analyze the project updates regularly and offer replacements if not satisfied.</li>\n            </ul>'),(83,'What kind of businesses can use Virto Commerce?','<ul>\n              <li>Virto Commerce is actually suitable for all businesses ranging from small startups to large\n                enterprises and particularly suited for businesses that require customization.</li>\n            </ul>'),(84,'Can third-party applications be integrated in Virto?','<ul>\n              <li>Yes, you can expand your ecommerce platforms functionalities and features as Virto supports\n                third-party integrations.</li>\n            </ul>'),(85,'What kind of feauture does Virto Commerce provide?','<ul>\n              <li>It offers a wide range of feautures such as inventory management, order processing, payment\n                processing, shipping, tax calculation, multiuple channel support, multiple channel support,\n                multi-lingual support, and also marketing tools.</li>\n            </ul>'),(86,'How does User Experience reflect on conversion rates?','<p>When your User Experience is great, your customers automatically engage with your website. A visually\n              appealing, interactive experience makes them want to stay, click, and purchase. This will also increase\n              their repeated visits to your website.</p>'),(87,'What is the difference between UX and UI? ','<p>UX focuses on the journey of the users and their overall experience including usability, accessibility,\n              as well as emotions. UI on the other hand deals with visual elements and layouts.</p>'),(88,'How can I create user-centered design?','<p>Reach out to us and get the best User Experience solutions for your brand to elevate and empower it in\n              the market. <a href=\"/contact-us\" class=\"text-dark\"> Contact us <span class=\"common-link\">  here</span></a>. </p>'),(89,'What is the role of storytelling in content experience?','<p>Storytelling is a powerful tool in content experience as it helps create emotional connections with the\n              audience, making the content more engaging and memorable.</p>'),(90,'What is the difference between content marketing and content experience?','<p>Content marketing focuses on creating and distributing content to attract and retain customers, while\n              content experience emphasizes how that content is presented and consumed for maximum impact.</p>'),(91,'How can I create engaging content experiences?','<p>Reach out to us and get the best Content Experience solutions for your brand to elevate and empower it in\n              the market. <a href=\"/contact-us\" class=\"text-dark\">Contact us <span class=\"common-link\">here</span>. </p>'),(92,'What role does technology play in commerce experience?','<p>Technology plays a significant role in enabling a smooth and efficient Commerce Experience. This includes website and app design, e-commerce platforms, payment processing systems, chatbots, and analytics tools to understand customer behavior.</p>'),(93,'What are some common challenges in optimizing Commerce Experience? ','<p>Common challenges include balancing aesthetics with functionality in website design, managing inventory and logistics for timely delivery, addressing customer service inquiries promptly, and staying up-to-date with evolving technology and trends.</p>'),(94,'How can I create engaging commerce experiences?','<p>Reach out to us and get the best Commerce Experience solutions for your brand to elevate and empower it in the market.<a href=\"/contact-us\" class=\"text-dark\">Contact us <span class=\"common-link\">here</span>.  </p>'),(95,'Is there a community of Umbraco users?',' <ul>\n              <li>Yes, Umbraco has a vibrant community of active developers, designers, etc. They offer support,\n                guidance, resources and help users learn and collaborate.</li>\n            </ul>'),(96,'Can you run a high-traffic site on Umbraco?','<ul>\n              <li>Yes, currently, your website through Umbraco can have 50,000 unique visitors per day.</li>\n            </ul>'),(97,'How do we know we are getting the right development team? ',' <ul>\n              <li>We analyze the job requirements and the business goals thoroughly. </li>\n              <li>We share the profiles of all our resources with the clients. </li>\n              <li>The resource allocation is always done based on the engagement model selected by the client. </li>\n              <li>We also analyze the project updates regularly and offer replacements if not satisfied.</li>\n            </ul>');
